'''Saigon Water Park''' is a former [[water park]] in [[Thủ Đức District]], [[Ho Chi Minh City]].<ref>[http://www.visitthemepark.net/saigon-water-park-s968/ visitthemepark.net]</ref> It was the first park of its kind built in the city. The park was situated on [[Saigon River]].
==Financial difficulties== The park encountered financial difficulty after the opening of a number of other competitor water parks in Ho Chi Minh City. Investors are in the process of re-zoning the land from leisure to residential.<ref>[http://www.vietnambreakingnews.com/2012/10/stop-construction-on-villa-project-city-water-park-told/ Stop construction on villa project, city water park told]</ref> All of the water park's equipment has been sold and removed. Many guide-books and travel websites still refer tourists to this tourist attraction, although it has closed.<ref>[https://www.virtualtourist.com/travel/Asia/Vietnam/Thanh_Pho_Ho_Chi_Minh/Ho_Chi_Minh_City-1470720/Things_To_Do-Ho_Chi_Minh_City-Saigon_Water_Park-BR-1.html virtualtourist]</ref>
